Blondetron smiles as she walks back into the room. "Mantella. I know she's 
after you. I heard a while back from a good friend of mine...Bobertron. Ever 
since I saw you, my soul has been fixated on you. I can't help but be in love 
with you. I know this is a change for  you, but I come from a different 
world."  She suddenly grabbs his titainium croth. "Kiss me" she ordered.
